# Write Models

If you are trying to do something completely new, you may wish to implement a model entirely from scratch within cvpods. However, in many situations you may be interested in modifying or extending some components of an existing model. Therefore, we provide an example of [Trident](https://git-core.megvii-inc.com/zhubenjin/cvpods_playground/tree/master/examples/TridentNet) it includes how to write your own code and combine it cvpods.
